```plantuml
@startuml madderle_Capstone-Realtime-Streaming-Analytics

actor User
participant "Twitter API" as TwitterAPI
participant "IEX API" as IEXAPI
participant "Twitter Service" as TwitterService
participant "IEX Service" as IEXService
participant "Manager Service" as ManagerService
participant "Redis" as Redis
participant "AWS Kinesis" as Kinesis
participant "MongoDB" as MongoDB
participant "S3 Storage" as S3
participant "SKLearn Model" as SKLearnModel
participant "Data Service" as DataService

User -> ManagerService: Start system
ManagerService -> Redis: Check market status
Redis --> ManagerService: Market open
ManagerService -> TwitterService: Start tweet collection
ManagerService -> IEXService: Start stock data collection

TwitterService -> TwitterAPI: Fetch tweets
TwitterAPI --> TwitterService: Return tweets
TwitterService -> Kinesis: Stream tweets
TwitterService -> MongoDB: Store tweets

IEXService -> IEXAPI: Fetch stock data
IEXAPI --> IEXService: Return stock data
IEXService -> Kinesis: Stream stock data
IEXService -> MongoDB: Store stock data

ManagerService -> SKLearnModel: Trigger prediction
SKLearnModel -> S3: Load model
S3 --> SKLearnModel: Return model
SKLearnModel -> MongoDB: Fetch data
MongoDB --> SKLearnModel: Return data
SKLearnModel -> SKLearnModel: Make predictions
SKLearnModel -> MongoDB: Store predictions

User -> DataService: Request data
DataService -> MongoDB: Query data
MongoDB --> DataService: Return data
DataService --> User: Display results

@enduml
```